<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>Jameela Jamil and Paul Mescal led the Brits for the virtual 72nd Emmys ceremony on Sunday night.</p>

<p>The actress, 34, whose show The Good Place is up for several awards, swapped her usual red carpet glamour for pyjamas and a sequin dressing gown.</p>

<p>Irish heartthrob and Normal People's nominee Paul Mescal, 24, meanwhile, was dressed to impress in a Louis Vuitton suit as he posed on the stairs ahead of the show. </p>

